creator: Airdropz Transport Limited
descriptionHtml:
Airdrops Taxi is an e-hailing transport system which focuses mostly on the airports trip and cummuting riders to and fro their destinations. One tap or a click makes your request easier and a ride comes directly to where you want it. The driver knows exactly where to go, and you can pay with either cash or card. With Airdrops.Taxi your destination is at your fingertips, just open the app and enter where you want to go, and a nearby driver will drive you there safely and reliably.

GET THERE FROM ALMOST ANYWHERE
Request a ride on demand or schedule one ahead of time. Airdrops.Taxi is available at airports and cities around the world, Airdrops.Taxi is an easy way to make your travel plans stress-free.

FIND THE RIDE YOU WANT
Airdrops.Taxi can help you find the perfect ride to fit your needs whether you’re looking for style, space, or affordability, Enjoy premium features with Airdrops.Taxi .

SEE PRICE ESTIMATES
Airdrops.Taxi, you can see your price estimate upfront before booking. That means you’ll always have an idea of what are paying before requesting your ride.

YOUR SAFETY DRIVES US BETTER
We’re committed to making every trip with Airdrops.Taxi safe and secured; that's why we built new safety features, a fascial recognition application system and OTP verification, for all our riders and drivers and updated our Community Guidelines for respectful and positive experiences.

- BOOK RIDE FOR 3RD PARTY
With our unique system you can book ride for your love once, and driver contact the 3rd party directly for the trip details.

- You can share your trip
Give your loved ones peace of mind while you’re on a trip—you can share your location and trip status so they know you made it to your destination.

TIP AND RATE YOUR DRIVER
After every ride, you can submit a rating along with comments. You can also let your driver know you appreciated your experience by adding a tip for them right in the app.

FOLLOW US:
Twitter: https://twitter.com/airdropstaxi
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/airdropstaxi/

With our unique system you can book ride for your love once, and driver contact the 3rd party directly for the trip details.

- You can share your trip
Give your loved ones peace of mind while you’re on a trip—you can share your location and trip status so they know you made it to your destination.

TIP AND RATE YOUR DRIVER
After every ride, you can submit a rating along with comments. You can also let your driver know you appreciated your experience by adding a tip for them right in the app.
